{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
 {\super\cf2\fs24 11}The {\scaps Lord} says:
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
For Edom\uc1\u8217*s three crimes \uc1\u8211*
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
no, four! \uc1\u8211* I will not rescind my judgment.
