{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
They have ripped open pregnant women in Gilead,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
in their lust for land.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
 {\super\cf2\fs24 14}So I will kindle a fire on the wall of Rabbah.
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
