Is not this indeed so, Israelites?
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
says the {\scaps Lord}.       
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
 {\super\cf2\fs24 12}But you made the Nazirites drink wine
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
and banned the prophets from prophesying.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
 {\super\cf2\fs24 13}Listen!
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
It is I who will make you groan in your places,      
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
as a wagon groans under its load of grain.   
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
 {\super\cf2\fs24 14}Then flight will fail the swift,  
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
and the strength of the strongest will be useless.
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
