\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
 {\super\cf2\fs24 15}the archer will not stand firm,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
the swift of foot will not escape,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
the horseman will not save his life.
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
 {\super\cf2\fs24 16}The bravest of warriors
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
