{\pard\sb360\sa360\fs36 The Basis of the Prophet\uc1\u8217*s Arraignment of Israel

\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
{\cf1 3}Hear this word
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\cf2\fs24 1}which the {\scaps Lord} has spoken against you, Israelites,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
against the whole nation that I brought out of Egypt:
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
 {\super\cf2\fs24 2}You alone have I cared for of all the nations of the world,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
this is why I will punish you for your crimes.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
 {\super\cf2\fs24 3}Do two walk together unless they agreed to meet?
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
 {\super\cf2\fs24 4}Does a lion roar in the forest when there is no prey for him?
