{\pard\sb360\sa360\fs36 Certain Destruction Awaiting Israel Unless She Seeks the Lord

\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
{\cf1 5}Hear the word which I take up against you, even a dirge, O house of Israel:
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
 {\super\cf2\fs24 2}Fallen, no more to rise, is the virgin Israel!
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
Hurled down upon her own soil she lies, with none to raise her!
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
 {\super\cf2\fs24 3}For thus saith the Lord the {\scaps Lord}:
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
The city that taketh the field with a thousand hath but a hundred left,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
And the one that taketh the field with a hundred bath but ten left.
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
 {\super\cf2\fs24 4}For thus saith the {\scaps Lord} to the house of Israel:
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
Seek me and live,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
 {\super\cf2\fs24 5}But seek not Bethel,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
And Gilgal do not enter,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
