\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
For Gilgal shall taste the gall of exile,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
And Bethel shall go to perdition.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
 {\super\cf2\fs24 6}Seek the {\scaps Lord} and live,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
Lest he cast fire on the house of Joseph,
\par}

